name: Korean Air 747-8B5 Intercontinental [HL7630] Landing at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
An old clip from my 2015 trip to Paine! Here we have Korean Air's first Boeing 747-8i touching down at Boeing's Everett facility back in July 2015 after a fairly long test flight. No ATC for this one, but enjoy this close up arrival!

Thanks for watching!
